{"name": "odoo-addon-partner-communication", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-partner-communication", "version": "16.0.1.0.0.2", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/sygel-technology/sy-partner-contact", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Select a communication channel in partners", "upload_time": 1733994045}, "documentation": ["```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.svg\n:alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n:target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl\n```\n\n# Partner Communication\n\nThis module allows to assign a communication channel to contacts. This information is transferred to sale order, purchase orders, pickings and invoices, but it can be freely edited.\n\n## Installation\n\nTo install this module, you need to:\n\n1. Only install\n\n## Configuration\n\nTo configure the stages of the opportunities that can be transferred, you need to:\n\n1. Go to Contact > Configuration > Communication Channel\n2. Create as many communication channels as needed.\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Select a communication channel in a contact, that will be applied to ale order, purchase orders, pickings and invoices. It can be edited if necessary.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs and errors are managed in [issues of GitHub](https://github.com/sygel-technology/sy-partner-contact/issues).\nIn case of problems, please check if your problem has already been\nreported. If you are the first to discover it, help us solving it by indicating\na detailed description [here](https://github.com/sygel-technology/sy-partner-contact/issues/new).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Manuel Regidor, Sygel\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Manuel Regidor \\<<mailto:manuel.regidor@sygel.es>>\n\n### Maintainer\n\nThis module is maintained by Sygel.\n\n```{image} https://www.sygel.es/logo.png\n:alt: Sygel\n:target: https://www.sygel.es\n```\n\nThis module is part of the [Sygel/sy-partner-contact](https://github.com/sygel-technology/sy-partner-contact).\n\nTo contribute to this module, please visit <https://github.com/sygel-technology>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models.partner_communication_channel", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 Manuel Regidor <manuel.regidor@sygel.es>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models.partner_communication_channel.PartnercCommunicationChannel", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models.partner_communication_channel.PartnercCommunicationChannel._name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models.partner_communication_channel.PartnercCommunicationChannel._description", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models.partner_communication_channel.PartnercCommunicationChannel.name", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 Manuel Regidor <manuel.regidor@sygel.es>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models.account_move", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models..account_move", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models.partner_communication_channel", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.partner_communication.models..partner_communication_channel", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.ad